com.panviva.util.pgc.rule

Class PartitionTargetProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.panviva.util.pgc.rule.MatchProperties
      • com.panviva.util.pgc.rule.PartitionTargetProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMatchProperties

    public class PartitionTargetProperties
extends MatchProperties
    This class is used set conditional match properties for a rule of type partition for a target_path task. Most of this can also be achieved using XPATH notation for the target path although the regular expression capability exposes the full power java based regular expressions
    Author:
    jcharles
